      • put

        public void put(Point point,
       I_UserInteract active)
        Put an interactive element inside a HashMap with a point value as the key. The key is used as a coordinate system. If an interactive element sits on more than one point then that object will be referenced on each point it resided.
        Parameters:
        point - the point an interactive element sits.
        active - the interactive element.
